{"tid":406854,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"10月至12月去北歐係咪凍到仆街?","createTime":"2017-09-20T03:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T10:36:45.000Z","uid":61703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c907527683e10c7f6956546f043bd87f045f942","tid":406854,"uid":61703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"黎緊既10月至12月會去北歐玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係網上面睇知道溫度係幾度至負幾度<br />\n但係都對呢個溫度無乜譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78ab847b5ce7d0b3efe8955599f95cfc18d5777","tid":406854,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n我8月去 已經覺得係香港冬天，落雨更加凍到震"},{"pid":"50f95919f86a39a715019d01f3ee8bdabbbce378","tid":406854,"uid":61703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係<br />\n<br />\n我8月去 已經覺得係香港冬天，落雨更加凍到震</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  包到隻粽咁去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b888b01d40f0ac64be69b011c1bd437f3bd7a76","tid":406854,"uid":10189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"其實北歐冬天無東歐咁凍"},{"pid":"09936ffe3b1498b02edae0ba9878a22515c5d280","tid":406854,"uid":61703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實北歐冬天無東歐咁凍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我由荷蘭開始經德國去丹麥一直北上,<br />\n之後由赫爾辛基經波羅的海三國落波蘭再返荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBOOK機票個陣完全無諗過溫度呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9af06582d7390da9aec96dbc0b5179f84ee721","tid":406854,"uid":88055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"舊年11月去 凍到仆街<br />\n仲有好多景點冬天唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算開，開放時都好短"},{"pid":"c3ab8cb3090a37c447ecdcd51ee04aaa4bd8c9f6","tid":406854,"uid":61703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊年11月去 凍到仆街<br />\n仲有好多景點冬天唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算開，開放時都好短</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好彩無乜景點想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但凍真係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0811ba730a9d10e113bb575ed4c8fa839e3cf5c5","tid":406854,"uid":135851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:55:42.000Z","msg":"我直頭聖誕果陣去瑞典 最熱都0度 最凍果日-23度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56ddaaec31f6b004dc431d77c6ed61be3ea45e1","tid":406854,"uid":123274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"11月尾去helsinki tallinn berlin<br />\n都係買完機票先醒起會凍到仆街<br />\n同埋日照時間短好快天黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7d1a23c06d2ef90e0f5883276af87cd07905f6","tid":406854,"uid":61703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我直頭聖誕果陣去瑞典 最熱都0度 最凍果日-23度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n體驗過負40度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎我都要再挑戰人體極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6518f0851ffb82c753e362ea040a2be87ef930","tid":406854,"uid":61703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>11月尾去helsinki tallinn berlin<br />\n都係買完機票先醒起會凍到仆街<br />\n同埋日照時間短好快天黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  飛票都買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我11月中就到Tallinn lu~~ 無緣相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1929ac08fb2c61f5989ac8cdbef020ad13f050cd","tid":406854,"uid":59707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"試過去helsinki -27度，我就著左heattech, 短tee, 冷衫，hoodie 厚褸，頸巾，手套各一，褲應該要打底<br />\n無風還好，有風應該頂唔住<br />\n仲有要注意電子器材保暖，太凍d電會食得好快<br />\n我就會擺暖包keep warm"},{"pid":"401bd223ac42d64c38d89c8db9894f8353ad74af","tid":406854,"uid":54432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過去helsinki -27度，我就著左heattech, 短tee, 冷衫，hoodie 厚褸，頸巾，手套各一，褲應該要打底<br />\n無風還好，有風應該頂唔住<br />\n仲有要注意電子器材保暖，太凍d電會食得好快<br />\n我就會擺暖包keep warm</blockquote><br />\n其實-10到-30個身我覺得分別唔太大<br />\n<br />\n反而係手腳耳仔同塊面會有明顯分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n年頭去瑞典北睇極光成-30我都係一件淘寶heattech,  一件普通長袖衫, 出面加件columbia titanium 1000td,  最外層加件播風防水風嬲已經夠用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相機我乜都冇包冇搞但d電都夠用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca5e9affe73493255d9c472d6373dce733eb183","tid":406854,"uid":61703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過去helsinki -27度，我就著左heattech, 短tee, 冷衫，hoodie 厚褸，頸巾，手套各一，褲應該要打底<br />\n無風還好，有風應該頂唔住<br />\n仲有要注意電子器材保暖，太凍d電會食得好快<br />\n我就會擺暖包keep warm</blockquote><br />\n其實-10到-30個身我覺得分別唔太大<br />\n<br />\n反而係手腳耳仔同塊面會有明顯分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n年頭去瑞典北睇極光成-30我都